summary: This mod lets you kill the Boss of the Aldmeri dominion
descriptionHtml:
A Stormcloak army is preparring to attack that thalmor castle at Fort Moonmeth will you join the Stormcloaks and eliminate the Thalmor? 

To start this mod 

go to the windhelm docks you will find a boat with a trapdoor open the 
trapdoor and your off to Fort Moonmeth but Remember the fort is already under attack so be Preparred for a fight 
On top of the Tower is the Mighty High Emperor Mealstien king of the Elf\'s. 



if thier is any bugs post them in the comments please
